
Description
-----------

Simply put, this script formats and returns mail log entries related to the
search term. This script outputs the logs lines by message id 


Usage
-----

  Usage:
    searchMailLogs.sh [-fti] <search_term>

  Options:

    -f
      Search for messages from <email_address>

    -t
      Search for messages to <email_address>

    -i
      Search for messages with Message ID

    -a
      Also search through archived mail logs

  Searches mail logs for anything matching specified terms

